          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Repay Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to direct the Department of Education to expand the student loan repayment options for new borrowers of William D. Ford Federal Direct Loans to include a simplified income-driven repayment plan. </p> <p>]]></text>
        </item>
